<section class="site-section site-section--divider" aria-labelledby="before-after-heading">
  <h2 id="before-after-heading">Before and after</h2>
  <div class="before-after-grid">
    <div class="before-after-col before">
      <p class="before-after-label">Before</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Info scattered across email, sheets, and apps</li>
        <li>Same details retyped in multiple places</li>
        <li>Reports built by hand when someone has time</li>
        <li>No clear view of what's stuck or due</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="before-after-col after">
      <p class="before-after-label">After</p>
      <ul>
        <li>One place to see what needs attention today</li>
        <li>Enter it once, it shows up where your team works</li>
        <li>Summaries and reports arrive on the schedule you set</li>
        <li>Built around how you operate, not a generic product</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .site-section--divider {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--site-border);
  }

  .site-section--divider h2 {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .before-after-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .before-after-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .before-after-col {
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--site-border);
    background: var(--site-surface);
  }

  .before-after-col.before {
    background: var(--site-surface-muted);
  }

  .before-after-label {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--site-text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .before-after-col ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .before-after-col li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--site-text-dim, #555);
    padding: 0.35rem 0 0.35rem 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .before-after-col li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.75rem;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--site-text-dim);
  }

  .before-after-col.after li::before {
    background: #4cc38a;
  }
</style>
